episodes.title: Church of Scientology backs out of deal to buy downtown Clearwater street
episodes.description: The Church of Scientology withdrew its application asking the City of Clearwater to vacate a downtown street ahead of the scheduled city council vote. Read more on WFLA.com

episodes.title: Clearwater Police accused of showing favor to Church of Scientology
episodes.description: The Clearwater Police Chief took to Facebook over the weekend, releasing a video where he answers allegations of being "used" and showing favor to the Church of Scientology, based in downtown Clearwater.
